Revision history for Device-Chip-AnalogConverters

0.09    2020-06-13
        [CHANGES]
         * Update to Object::Pad 0.27
            + BUILD block syntax
            + package+class declaration to keep metadata parsers happy

0.08    2019-09-07 22:15:15
        [CHANGES]
         * Avoid Data::Bitfield's "bytes-BE" format as it is due to be changed

0.07    2019-01-04 21:49:33
        [CHANGES]
         * Rewrite logic back to Future::AsyncAwait again

0.06    2018-11-18 01:14:00
        [CHANGES]
         * Revert Future::AsyncAwait experimentation
         * Document some standard ADC and DAC methods
         * Added drivers for MCP3221 and DAC7571
         * Created generic adc.pl and dac.pl example wrapper scripts

        [BUGFIXES]
         * Fix MAX11200's UB config bit decoding

0.05    2018-01-18 16:19:14
        [CHANGES]
         * Rewrite logic to use Future::AsyncAwait as demonstration

0.04    2017-11-11 00:46:06
        [CHANGES]
         * Added MAX11200 driver

0.03    2017-09-20 01:52:22
        [CHANGES]
         * Added AD5691R driver
         * Noted that ADS1115 can also drive ADS101x family chips

0.02    2017-08-24 19:06:59
        [CHANGES]
         * Declare dependence on Data::Bitfield (RT122887)
         * Generally improved dependency declarations in Build.PL

0.01    2017-08-23 12:21:19
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
